Package com.intellij.util.lang

Class UrlClassLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.ClassLoader
      • com.intellij.util.lang.UrlClassLoader
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AntResourcesClassLoader, PluginClassLoader

    public class UrlClassLoader
extends java.lang.ClassLoader
    A class loader that allows for various customizations, e.g. not locking jars or using a special cache to speed up class loading. Should be constructed using build() method.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  UrlClassLoader.Builder 
      static interface  UrlClassLoader.CachePool
      An interface for a pool to store internal caches that can be shared between different class loaders, if they contain the same URLs in their class paths. The implementation is subject to change so one shouldn't rely on it.
      static interface  UrlClassLoader.CachingCondition
      A condition to customize the caching policy when using UrlClassLoader.CachePool.
